casebody.data:
Monday, November 13, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-1551. State ex rel. Waldick v. Williams.

Van Wert County, No. 15-95-6. On October 30,1995, appellant filed a memorandum opposing appellee’s motion to expedite which was due October 27,1995. S.CtJPrac.R. XTV(1)(C) prohibits the filing of a document that is not timely tendered for filing. Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, effective November 8, 1995, that appellant’s memorandum opposing appellee’s motion to expedite be, and hereby is, stricken.
